<template>
  <v-list>
    <v-subheader inset>主菜单</v-subheader>

    <v-list-item to="/Dashboard">
    <v-list-item-icon>
      <v-icon>mdi-home</v-icon>
    </v-list-item-icon>
    <v-list-item-title>仪表盘</v-list-item-title>
    </v-list-item>

    <listItem :listData="stu"></listItem>
    <listItem :listData="teach"></listItem>
    <listItem :listData="subject"></listItem>
    <v-divider ></v-divider>
  </v-list>
</template>

<script>
import listItem from "@/views/listItem";
export default {
name: "navigation",
  data(){
    return{
      stu:{
        data: [
          ['学生名单', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline','/nameList'],
          ['学生信息', 'mdi-cog-outline','/information'],
          ['添加学生', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline','/add'],
          ['修改学生', 'mdi-cog-outline','/modify'],
        ],
        title:'学生',
        icon:'mdi-home'
      },

      teach:{
        data: [
          ['老师名单', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['老师信息', 'mdi-cog-outline'],
          ['添加老师', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['修改老师', 'mdi-cog-outline'],
        ],
        title:'老师',
        icon:'mdi-home'
      },

      subject:{
        data: [
          ['学科名单', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['添加学科', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['修改学科', 'mdi-cog-outline'],
        ],
        title:'学科',
        icon:'mdi-home'
      },
      account:{
        data: [
          ['收费', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['费用', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
          ['工资', 'mdi-cog-outline'],
        ],
        title:'账目',
        icon:'mdi-home'
      },

  }
  },
  components:{
    listItem
  }

}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
